@startuml
title ATM Control - PIN Validation and User Interaction

[*] --> Idle

state Idle
state "Waiting for PIN" as WaitingForPIN
state ValidatingPIN
state "Try Again" as TryAgain
state Confiscating
state Ejecting

Idle --> WaitingForPIN : Card Inserted / Get PIN

WaitingForPIN --> ValidatingPIN : PIN Entered / Validate PIN
ValidatingPIN --> WaitingForPIN : Invalid PIN / Invalid PIN Prompt
ValidatingPIN --> TryAgain : Third Invalid PIN, Card Stolen, Card Expired / Confiscate, Update Status

TryAgain --> WaitingForPIN : Try Again / Get PIN
ValidatingPIN --> Ejecting : Cancel / Eject
WaitingForPIN --> Ejecting : Cancel / Eject

@enduml
